      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly way to get from A to B? This vehicle has certainly lived a full life and shows significant wear and tear both inside and out, but it's ready for a new owner who appreciates a bargain! It's a great opportunity for someone handy looking for a low-cost entry into vehicle ownership. Sold as-is, this car is priced to move and offers honest, simple transportation for the right buyer!",
