    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of her\u2014she\u2019s honestly in pristine, showroom condition and drives like a total dream. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let her go, but I\u2019m looking for a great new home for this beauty. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
