    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is an investment-grade example that looks and smells as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and matte, free from any bolster wear or UV fading, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, documented in a comprehensive binder. Always stored in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its model year. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
